{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以沒落時的星宿盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"你們的朋友，既不迷誤，又未迷信，"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"也未隨私欲而言。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"這只是他所受的啟示，"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"教授他的，是那強健的、"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"有力的，故他達到全美。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"他在東方的最高處，"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"然後他漸漸接近而降低，"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"他相距兩張弓的長度，或更近一些。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"他把他所應啟示的啟示他的僕人，"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"他的心沒有否認他所見的。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"難道你們要為他所見的而與他爭論嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"他確已見他二次下降，"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"在極境的酸棗樹旁，"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"那裡有歸宿的樂園。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"當酸棗樹蒙上一層東西的時候，"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"眼未邪視，也未過分；"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"他確已看見他的主的一部分最大的跡象。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"他們告訴我吧！拉特和歐薩，"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"以及排行第三，也是最次的默那，怎麼是真主的女兒呢？"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"難道男孩歸你們，女孩卻歸真主嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"然而，這是不公平的分配。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"這些偶像只是你們和你們的祖先所定的名稱，真主並未加以証實，他們只是憑猜想和私欲。正道確已從他們的主降臨他們。"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"難道人希望什麼就有什麼？"},{"SurahNumber":53,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"後世和今世，都是真主的。"}]}